quran[182]{c,v,t}:
  37,1,Ndarahiye kubatonze imirongo n’iyindi
  37,2,Kandi kuri barya batuza amabi yose
  37,3,Kandi kuri barya basoma ubutumwa bw’Imana
  37,4,Mu vy’ukuri Imana yanyu niyo yonyene gusa
  37,5,"Umuremyi\tw’Amajuru\tn’Isi\thamwe\tnibimwo\thagati\tyavyo\tkandi n’Umuremyi w’ubuseruko bwose"
  37,6,Ntankeka twebwe twarasharije Ijuru riri hafi kw’isharizo ry’Inyenyeri
  37,7,Nukuyi kingira n’amashetani yataye umurongo
  37,8,"Ntibashobore\tkwumviriza\tibiremwa\tvyeranda\tno\tmugihe\tbirukanywe kumpande zose"
  37,9,"Bazoshirwa kure, kandi bazoba bafise n’ibihano bitazoba vako"
  37,10,"Dukuye\tmwo\tuwusahuye\tikintu\tgitoyi\tmunyuma\tagaca\takurikiranwa n’igishirira gisayangana"
  37,11,"Nimubabaze muti:- mbega nibo bafise ishusho rikomeye cane canke barya twaremye, ntankeka ni twebwe twabaremye tubakuye mw’ivu rimatanye n’irindi"
  37,12,Mbega uratangara nabo babifata minenerwe
  37,13,Mugihe batujijwe ntiba gondozwa
  37,14,Mugihe babonye ibitangaro vyacu babifata minenerwe
  37,15,"Nukuvuga\tbati:-\tntivyari\tkuba\tibi\tvyose\tatari\tuko\tari\tuburozi\tburi k’umugaragaro"
  37,16,Mbega mugihe tuzosandaba nukuba ivu n’amagufa niko kuzoba ari ukuri kukuzurwa
  37,17,N’abatama bacu bakera
  37,18,"Vuga uti:- egome muri ico gihe muzoba muri mubihano bitazoba vako"
  37,19,Iyo mumuriro udahera hazoba hari induru yurutavana ko munyuma yaho bazobona umuhero w’Isi washitse
  37,20,"Bazovuga bati:- yo! Uwu niwo wamusi w’impembo"
  37,21,Uwu niwo musi wugucibwa urubanza mwahora muhakana
  37,22,Begeranye bamwe bahemukiye imitima yabo hamwe n’abagenzi babo hamwe nabo bahora basenga
  37,23,"Aho\tgusenga\tImana\tnimuba\trongore\tmunzira\tyomu\tmuriro\tudahera witiriwe Jahannamu"
  37,24,Nimuba hagarike mu vy’ukuri bazobazwa
  37,25,Mufise iki ko mutarokorana
  37,26,Kuri uwo musi bazoteterwa bimwe bitarabaho
  37,27,Bazokwinjira babazanya bamwe n’abandi
  37,28,"Bavuga\tbati:-\tmu\tvy’ukuri\tmwebwe\tmwamye\tmudushikira\tmunzira z’ukuri"
  37,29,"Nabo bishure bati:- ahubwo mwebwe bonyene ntimwari muba Isilamu"
  37,30,Ntabubasha twari dufise hejuru yanyu mugabo mwebwe nyene mwari mubataye umurongo w’ukuri
  37,31,Rero intahe y’Umuremyi wacu iramaze gucibwa ntankeka tuzoyihonja
  37,32,Nitwebwe bonyene twabatakaje tukaba twari mubantu bazimiye
  37,33,Rero mu vy’ukuri kuri uwo musi bazoba bari mubihano bakoranijwe hamwe
  37,34,Uku niko tuzogira abo bataye umurongo
  37,35,"Mugihe\tbahora\tbabwirwa\tyuko\tatayindi\tMana\titegerezwa\tgusengwa bimwe vy’ukuri atari Imana y’ukuri baguma banana"
  37,36,"Nukuvuga bati:- yo! twebwe dusige Imana zacu kubera uyo ategura amajambo y’ubuhizi nawe ari umusazi"
  37,37,"Ahubwo\tyaje\tafise\tukuri\tnukwemeza\tintumwa\tz’Imana\tzose\tzabaye imbere yiwe"
  37,38,Mu vy’ukuri mwebwe ntankeka muzohonja ibihano bibabaza cane
  37,39,Kandi ntimuzohembwa atari kuvyo mwahora mugira
  37,40,Dukuyemwo abantu beranda b’Imana bagize ibikorwa vyabo vyiza
  37,41,Abo bantu nibo bazoronka imigisha yabo bwite
  37,42,Ivyamwa vy’ubwoko bwose kandi baterwe n’iteka ntangere
  37,43,Mumirima y’imigisha myiza
  37,44,Bari hejuru y’ubusaswa barabana n’abandi amaso kuyandi
  37,45,Bakikuzwa n’ibirahuri birimwo ibinyobwa vyiza cane
  37,46,Vyera derere bifise n’akanovera kuri abo bantu babinywera mwo
  37,47,"Kuri\tivyo\tbinywobwa\tntangorane\tn’imwe\tzizoba\tzirimwo\tcanke ugutakaza ubwenge"
  37,48,Bazoba bari kumwe n’abapfasoni bafise amaso meza manini maniniya
  37,49,Abo bapfasoni bameze nk’amagi yabitswe neza
  37,50,Bazohura bamwe n’abandi babazanya
  37,51,"Hanyuma avuge umuvugizi umwe muribo ati:- mu vy’ukuri jewe nari mfise umugenzi"
  37,52,"Uwahora ambwira ati:- mbega wewe uri muri bamwe bemera\tImana yabo y’ukuri"
  37,53,"Yuko\tmugihe\ttwebwe\ttuzo\tsandaba\tnukuba\tivu\tn’amagufa\tmbega twebwe tuzorihwa"
  37,54,"Nawe azovuga ati:- mbega muzo mu runguruka"
  37,55,Nawe azo runguruka aze amubone ari hagati y’umuriro udahera witiriwe Jahannamu
  37,56,"Hanyuma aze amubwire ati:- ndarahiye kw’izina ry’Imana wewe wari wegereje kunzimiza"
  37,57,"Iyo\titaba\timigisha\ty’Umuremyi\twanje\tntankeka\tnari\tkuba\tmubo shengezwa n’ibihano vyo mumuriro udahera"
  37,58,Mbega na twebwe turi mu bantu bazo subira kwitaba Umuremyi wacu
  37,59,"Atari\turupfu\trwacu\trwaho\thambere\tkandi\ttwebwe\tntituzo\tsubira guhanwa"
  37,60,Ntankeka iyi niyo ntsinzi niniya
  37,61,Rero akarorero nkaka niko bogira abo bogira
  37,62,"Mbega ikaze nkiri siryiza, canke kuronka igiti citiriwe Zaqqum"
  37,63,Mu vy’ukuri twebwe twagize ico giti nk’igihano caba hemukiye imitima yabo
  37,64,"Mu\tvy’ukuri\tico\tn’igiti\tkivuye\thagati\ty’umuriro\tudahera\twitiriwe Jahannamu"
  37,65,Ivyamwa vy’ico giti bimeze nk’imitwe y’amashetani
  37,66,Ntankeka bazofungura kuri ico giti no kurico buzuze inda zabo
  37,67,Hanyuma ntankeka bazo shikirwa kubera uburure bw’ico giti n’uruvange rw’amazi y’amarike
  37,68,Hanyuma mu vy’ukuri ingaruka yabo bantu yazoba ari ayo mumuriro udahera witiriwe Jahannamu
  37,69,Mu vy’ukuri basanze abavyeyi babo barazimiye
  37,70,Nabo nyene baca batwarwa nugukurikira ingendo zabo
  37,71,Kandi ntankeka abantu benshi bakera barazimiye imbere yabo
  37,72,Mu vy’ukuri twararungitse abagabisha kuri abo bantu
  37,73,Rero nurabe uko yabaye amaherezo yabo bantu batujijwe
  37,74,Atari abagamburutsi b’Imana bigiriye ibikorwa vyabo vyiza
  37,75,"Mu\tvy’ukuri\tintumwa\ty’Imana\tNuhu\t(iii)\tyaraduteye\takamo, n’abamwitavye b’intungane tumeze gute twebwe"
  37,76,Twaramurokoye hamwe n’abantu biwe bari muvyago bihambaye
  37,77,Twarahezagiye umuryango wiwe ngo babe aribo baguma kw’Isi
  37,78,Duca tumusigira ku bantu baje munyuma yiwe
  37,79,Amahoro y’intumwa y’Imana Nuhu (iii) asasagare kw’Isi yose
  37,80,Mu vy’ukuri uku niko duhemba abagira ineza
  37,81,Mu vy’ukuri yari mubantu bacu bemeye Imana yabo y’ukuri
  37,82,Munyuma yaho niho twaca twibiza bamwe n’abandi
  37,83,Mu vy’ukuri intumwa y’Imana Ibrahimu (III) yari mumurwi wiwe
  37,84,Yarayikoreye idini y’Umuremyi wiwe n’umutima mwiza cane
  37,85,"Yaramubwiye\tSe\twiwe\thamwe\tn’abantu\tbiwe\tati:-\tmbega\tmwebwe musenga iki"
  37,86,"Kuvyiyadukije gusa vy’amamana aho yobaye Imana y’ukuri, nizo Mana mwipfuza"
  37,87,None n’ibihe vyiyumviro vyanyu hejuru y’Umuremyi w’ibiremwa vyose
  37,88,Hanyuma yaciye yitegereza mu kwitegereza kunyenyeri
  37,89,"Avuga ati:- mu vy’ukuri jewe ndarwaye"
  37,90,Nabo baramuretse gutyo baca bamuha ibitugu barigira
  37,91,"Nawe aca agenda mumpisho no ku Mana zabo azibwira ati:- mbega mufise iki ko muda fungura"
  37,92,Mubaye gute ko mutavuga
  37,93,Hanyuma arahindukira abakubita n’ukuboko kwiwe kw’iburyo
  37,94,Baca baza n’ingoga na ningoga
  37,95,"Aca ababwira ati:- oh! Mbega musenga muvyo mwibaziye kubwanyu n’amaboko yanyu"
  37,96,Mugihe Imana ariyo yabaremwye hamwe nivyo mugira vyose
  37,97,"Nabo\tbishura\tbati:-\tnimu\tmwubakire\tinyubakwa\thanyuma\tmu mujugunyire muri uwo mukomezwa"
  37,98,"Rero bashatse kumu girira amarorerwa, mugabo duca\ttuba girira kuba aribo badebukiwe"
  37,99,"Nayo intumwa y’Imana Ibrahimu (iii) yababwiye iti:- jewe ndagiye ku Muremyi wanje niwe azondongora"
  37,100,"Ewe Muremyi wanje, numpe mu bantu bagira ineza"
  37,101,Niho twamuha inkuru nziza y’ikibondo gitekanye
  37,102,"Mugihe yashika kurugero rw’ukugenda nukugaruka ari kumwe nawe niho yamubwira ati:- ewe kibondo canje, mu vy’ukuri jewe nabonye mundoto zanje yuko no kubaga, rero nawe niwiyumvire neza, none wewe ubibona gute? Nawe amwishura ati:- ewe data wanje nugire nk’uko wategetswe nanje uzonsanga Imana ibishatse ndimu bantu batenyenya"
  37,103,Bose hamwe uko ari babiri mugihe biyemeza imbere y’Imana nuguca amuryamika hasi kugira ngo amubage
  37,104,"Muri uwo mwanya isase twaciye tumu hamagara duti:- ewe ntumwa y’Imana Ibrahimu (iii)"
  37,105,"Uramaze kwemeza yandoto yawe, mu vy’ukuri uku rero niko duhemba abagira neza bose"
  37,106,Ntankeka iri n’igeragezo riri k’umugaragaro
  37,107,Rero duca dukabisha n’igikoko cukubarwa gifise iteka ntangere
  37,108,Duca tumusigira kubaje munyuma yiwe
  37,109,Amahoro y’Imana abe kuntumwa y’Imana Ibrahimu (iii)
  37,110,Uku niko duhemba abantu bagira ineza bose
  37,111,Ntankeka yari mubantu bacu bemeye Imana yabo y’ukuri
  37,112,"Hanyuma\ttwamuciriye\tagace\tyuko\tazokwibaruka\tintumwa\ty’Imana Is’haqa (iii) n’intumwa muntumwa z’ abagira ineza"
  37,113,"Duca turamu hezagira hamwe n’intumwa y’Imana Is’haqa (iii) hamwe no muruvyaro rwabo, kuko aribo babaye mubagira ineza. hamwe n’abahemukiye imitima yabo bimwe bigaragara"
  37,114,Mu vy’ukuri twebwe twarabagiriye impuhwe intumwa y’Imana Mussa (iii) hamwe n’intumwa y’Imana Haruna (iii)
  37,115,Duca turaba rokora hamwe n’abantu babo mugihe bari mungorane zidasanzwe
  37,116,Duca tubakingira nabo baca baba bene intsinzi nyakuri
  37,117,Bose uko ari babiri twabahaye igitabu gitanga umuco
  37,118,Duca turabarongora munzira igororotse
  37,119,Hanyuma duca tubasigira mubaje munyuma yabo
  37,120,Amahoro y’Imana abe kuntumwa y’Imana Mussa (iii) hamwe na Haruna (iii)
  37,121,Ntankeka uku niko duhemba abagira ineza
  37,122,Ntankeka bari mubantu bacu bemeye Imana yabo y’ukuri
  37,123,"Mu vy’ukuri, intumwa y’Imana Il’yaasiiyn (iii) yari muntumwa z’Imana"
  37,124,"Mugihe yabwira abantu biwe ati:- mbega mwebwe ntimutinya"
  37,125,"Mutabaza isanamu ryitwa Baa’la, mukareka gusaba umwiza wabaremyi"
  37,126,"Imana\tariyo\tmuremyi\twanyu\tn’Umuremyi\tw’abavyeyi\tbanyu\tbaho hambere"
  37,127,Baramu hakanye ntankeka rero bazo shengezwa mubihano
  37,128,Dukuyemwo abantu b’Imana basukuwe nayo nyene
  37,129,Twamusigiye kubaje munyuma yiwe
  37,130,Amahoro y’Imana abe kuntumwa y’Imana Il’yaasiiyn (iii)
  37,131,Ntankeka uku niko duhemba abagira ineza
  37,132,Mu vy’ukuri yari mubantu bacu bemera Imana yabo bimwe vy’ukuri
  37,133,Mu vy’ukuri intumwa y’Imana Lutwi (iii) yari muntumwa z’Imana
  37,134,Mugihe twamurokora hamwe n’abantu biwe bose
  37,135,Dukuye mwo umukenyezi ashaje mubasigaye inyuma
  37,136,Hanyuma niho twahonya abandi
  37,137,Mu vy’ukuri mwama mubacako mugitondo
  37,138,"No mw’ijoro nyene, mbega mwebwe ntimutegera"
  37,139,Mu vy’ukuri intumwa y’Imana Yunusu (iii) yari muntumwa z’Imana
  37,140,Mugihe yirukira mubwato bwikoreye ibintu vyinshi
  37,141,Baca bagira amatora aca aba mubatsinzwe nuguca atabwa mumazi
  37,142,Mukanya ifi ica iramumira mugihe yari muba taweko umwikomo
  37,143,Iyo ataba yari mubantu basenga Imana yiwe y’ukuri
  37,144,"Ntankeka\tyari\tkuguma\tmunda\ty’iyofi\tkugeza\tk’umusi\twizurwa ry’abantu bose"
  37,145,"Mugabo\ttwaciye\ttumujugunya\tkunkengera\tz’ikiyaga\tnawe\taremvye cane"
  37,146,Duca tumu nagishiriza uruyuzi rw’itango yaguma afungura
  37,147,Twaramutwaye ku bantu ibihumbi ijana n’abarenga
  37,148,"Baca baremera, nukuba nezereza kugeza kugihe caho basandabira"
  37,149,"Nimu\tbabaze\tmuti:-\tmbega\tUmuremyi\twawe\tniwe\tafise\tibibondo vy’abigeme nabo bakaba bafise ibibomdo vy’abahungu"
  37,150,"Mbega\ttwebwe\ttwaremye\tAbamarayika\tkuba\tyuko\taribo\tbakenyezi nabo bakaba ivyabona"
  37,151,Muragabe ku vyiyadukiza kuribo n’ivyo bavuga
  37,152,"Imana yaravyaye, mu vy’ukuri kuribo ntankeka n’ababeshi"
  37,153,Yoba yaratoye ibibondo vy’abigeme gusumba ibibondo vy’abahungu
  37,154,Mubayeho gute! Muca urubanza gute
  37,155,Yo! Mbega mwebwe aho muri ntimwibuka
  37,156,Canke mwebwe murafise ivyemezo biri k’umugaragaro
  37,157,Nimuzane igitabu canyu ni mwaba muvugisha ukuri
  37,158,"Nabo bashizeho imiryango hagati yabo n’ibisigo, n’ivyo bisigo vyari vyamaze kumenya yuko atankeka kuribo bazo shengezwa"
  37,159,Imana iri kure n’ingene bayihayagiza
  37,160,Dukuye mwo abantu beranda batowe n’Imana
  37,161,Rero ntankeka mwebwe hamwe nabo musenga
  37,162,Ntimushobora kuba zimiza
  37,163,Atari bamwe bazo kwinjira mu muriro udahera
  37,164,Ntan’umwe muri twebwe atari uko afise ubwicaro bwiwe buzwi
  37,165,Mu vy’ukuri muri twebwe harimwo abatonda ku mirongo
  37,166,Hariho n’abandi muri twebwe bahayagiza Imana y’ukuri
  37,167,Mu vy’ukuri bamye bavuga
  37,168,Iyo tuba dufise igitabu nkuko babifise ba bantu baho hambere
  37,169,Ntankeka twari kuba mu bantu beranda b’Imana bisukuye
  37,170,Ico gitabu baragi hakanye rero ubu vuba bazomenya
  37,171,Kandi ntankeka ijambo ryacu riramaze gushika ku bantu bacu bahawe ubutumwa
  37,172,Yuko aribo bazo rokorwa
  37,173,N’ingabo zacu nizo zizo tsinda
  37,174,Rero nimu bareke kure mu mwanya mutoyi gusa
  37,175,Kandi mu bitegereze gusa nabo ubu vuba bazobona
  37,176,Yoh! barahimiriza ibihano vyacu
  37,177,Rero mugihe bizo manuka kurubuga rwabo hazoba hari mugitondo kitari ciza ku bantu batujijwe
  37,178,Nimu bareke mumwanya mutoyi gusa
  37,179,"Nurabe gusa, nabone ubu vuba bazobona"
  37,180,"Umuremyi\twawe\tari\tkure\tnivyo,\tUmuremyi\tw’iteka\thamwe\tn’ivyo bayihayagiza ko"
  37,181,N’amahoro y’Imana asasagare kuntumwa z’Imana zose
  37,182,"Nihayagizwa ryose ryiza niry’Imana, Umuremyi w’ibiremwa vyose"